com.facebook.litho.animation

Class TransitionAnimationBinding

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.litho.animation.TransitionAnimationBinding
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnimationBinding
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BezierTransition, SpringTransition, TimingTransition

    public abstract class TransitionAnimationBinding
extends Object
    Base class for defining animations for transitions between states of the component hierarchy. Subclasses should define their animation by creating a GraphBinding in setupBinding(com.facebook.litho.animation.Resolver).
